'''雷基象'''是最大的[[象|大象]]之一，頭顱短而高，象牙不大，其前肢較現代象長，眼窩低。分布於[[东部非洲|東非]]和[[阿拉伯半岛|阿拉伯半島]]。從350萬年前[[上新世|上新世]]出現，一直到50萬年前滅絕。根据摩洛哥发现的一头四十岁的雄象化石，它肩高可达{{convert|4.27|m|ft}}，重可达{{convert|12.3|t|}}。<ref name="proboscideans">{{Cite journal | last1 = Larramendi | first1 = A. | last2 =  | first2 =  | year = 2016 | title = Shoulder height, body mass and shape of proboscideans | journal = Acta Palaeontologica Polonica | volume = 61 | issue =  | pages =  | publisher =  | jstor =  | doi = 10.4202/app.00136.2014 | url = https://www.app.pan.pl/archive/published/app61/app001362014.pdf | format =  | accessdate =  | archive-date = 2016-08-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160824042509/http://www.app.pan.pl/archive/published/app61/app001362014.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>Marinheiro, J., Mateus, O., Alaoui, A., Amani, F., Nami, M., & Ribeiro, C. (2014). New Quaternary fossil sites from the Middle Atlas of Morocco. Comunicações Geológicas, 101(Especial I), 485-488.</ref>

